<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="informed-adj">informed <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'fɔːmd/    美 /ɪn'fɔːrmd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>有知识的；见多识广的；消息灵通的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The child was not old enough to make an <strong>informed choice</strong>.
这个孩子年纪还小，无法做出明智的选择。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We will <strong>keep</strong> you <strong>informed of</strong> any development.
有任何进展我们都会随时通知你。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I became <strong>well-informed about</strong> the subject.
我很了解这个主题。</p></div></div>